    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/c598f3-79/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607922545089315414&sectionId=607922545190830678)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLlzIenFpW_text","label":"ggLlzIenFpW_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#151515;\">Why </span><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Grinding &amp; Clenching</span><span style=\"color:#151515;\"> Shouldn't Be Ignored</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYeEheYm5x_text","label":"ggYeEheYm5x_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Tooth Damage &amp; Sensitivity</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCzv6G9-eN_text","label":"ggCzv6G9-eN_text","default":"<p>Enamel doesn't regenerate. Grinding wears it down permanently, exposing inner layers and causing sensitivity to hot, cold, and sweet foods.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggvqLg6zjw_text","label":"gggvqLg6zjw_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Headaches &amp; Facial Fatigue</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl71JLespp_text","label":"ggl71JLespp_text","default":"<p>Chronic jaw muscle tension often radiates to the temples and forehead, causing persistent tension headaches and facial discomfort.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ3DnGlD-__text","label":"ggZ3DnGlD-__text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Morning Jaw Tightness</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6GJbX6CM9_text","label":"gg6GJbX6CM9_text","default":"<p>Waking up with a sore, stiff jaw is a clear sign of overnight clenching. This tension can last throughout the day and affect eating and speaking.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMA-nF0TQw_text","label":"ggMA-nF0TQw_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#E5C185;\">Poor Sleep Quality</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaX5TeAaCU_text","label":"ggaX5TeAaCU_text","default":"<p>Grinding disrupts your sleep architecture, preventing deep, restorative rest. Poor sleep increases stress, which worsens grinding—a vicious cycle.</p>"}],
